  <brief_title>Para-vertebral Dexmedetomidine and the Incidence of Postoperative Chronic Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Para-Vertebral Dexmedetomidine in Video-Assisted Thoracic Surgeries for Acute and Chronic Pain Prevention; A Randomized Double Blinded Clinical Trial</official_title>
